# Real .env files (git-ignored by this project's root .gitignore) hold
# secrets and per-environment values — never commit a real one.
#
# A DIFFERENT dedicated schema than the previous topic's
# "node_express_learning" — Prisma Migrate needs to fully own a schema's
# history via its own migration files. Pointing migrate dev at a schema
# that already has a table Migrate doesn't know about (like the previous
# topic's db-push-created "Task" table) makes it detect "drift" and
# offer to reset the WHOLE schema to reconcile. Verified directly while
# building this topic. See build-conventions.md for the full story.
DATABASE_URL="postgres://user:password@host:5432/postgres?schema=node_express_learning_migrations"
